ybe bipolar disorder come to mind because they can have similar symptoms.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040159,0.061221,0.076461,0.088241,0.095384,0.10024,0.10275,0.1006,0.10036,0.099654,0.082014,0.052909],"unified_progress":[0.044225,0.066715,0.081949,0.091658,0.096319,0.10004,0.099873,0.096648,0.092068,0.088821,0.0775,0.064184]},{"section":9,"text":"Let's dig deeper into what's going on here.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11825,0.093915,0.086905,0.077601,0.077832,0.079346,0.080863,0.08867,0.079152,0.053726,0.055644,0.1081],"unified_progress":[0.20641,0.079515,0.064686,0.064526,0.074032,0.073955,0.097345,0.082098,0.078957,0.06371,0.058882,0.055883]},{"section":10,"text":"During the mental exam, she shows a flat affect.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.084452,0.090757,0.097097,0.10262,0.1022,0.096757,0.089234,0.079414,0.072211,0.070456,0.064066,0.050729],"unified_progress":[0.077453,0.10894,0.07271,0.095955,0.097177,0.097343,0.089104,0.085331,0.07862,0.073554,0.066967,0.05685]},{"section":11,"text":"Hmm, that means her emotions seem really blunted.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.05231,0.092407,0.10503,0.11263,0.1113,0.10581,0.096814,0.083583,0.076621,0.068136,0.056722,0.038637],"unified_progress":[0.05261,0.083879,0.095498,0.10047,0.10503,0.099071,0.096605,0.088699,0.084665,0.074279,0.065462,0.053732]},{"section":12,"text":"This isn't just a one-off thing; it's consistent.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.13162,0.10166,0.0946,0.083157,0.081221,0.080885,0.079592,0.084693,0.07367,0.048356,0.048285,0.092263],"unified_progress":[0.21459,0.083775,0.069413,0.066964,0.076382,0.075063,0.086591,0.080843,0.075763,0.061693,0.056154,0.052769]},{"section":13,"text":"And then there's thought insertion.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.04672,0.077906,0.098271,0.11105,0.1